# Electron / electron-builder 二进制从国内镜像下载
# 根因:Electron postinstall (node install.js) 用 @electron/get 走 node https 直连
# GitHub releases 大文件,不继承 git 代理、环境变量代理也为空 → 国内裸连卡死。
# 此处只覆盖二进制来源,不改 npm registry(其余依赖仍走官方源)。
electron_mirror=https://npmmirror.com/mirrors/electron/
electron_builder_binaries_mirror=https://npmmirror.com/mirrors/electron-builder-binaries/
